snippet.title: Tropico 6 - Spitter DLC | Trailer US
snippet.description:
It’s all about fame and prestige. Nobody knows this better than a self-declared despot...uh, statesman, such as El Presidente. Tropico 6’s second DLC skyrockets you into the world of stardom and illustriousness.
